  "newspaper_id": "lankadeepa-lk",
  "url": "https://www.lankadeepa.lk/news/\u0dc3\u0ddd\u0db7\u0dd2\u0dad-\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dd2\u0dba\u0ddd-\u0d85\u0db1\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd4-\u0d85\u0d9f\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dd2/101-616493",
  "time_ut": 1657906374,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0dc3\u0ddd\u0db7\u0dd2\u0dad \u0dc4\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dd2\u0dba\u0ddd \u0d85\u0db1\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd4 \u0d85\u0d9f\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sobhita Thero warns",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The seizure of automatic weapons in the possession of army soldiers in the struggle area was a serious incident. Did the weapons fall into the hands of underworld gangs? In the hands of mobs? When and where do they burn? Dr. Omalpe Sobitha Thero warned in Embilipitiya that the struggle was a serious issue.",
        "The young people of the struggle as well as the civilians should keep this matter in mind and work ahead. For whom will the missing weapons be returned? According to the information reported to us, there are debates, ideologies, attacks and disputes between the groups that have emerged among the fighters.",
        "Under such a situation, will the lost lives be directed at the respective leaders, will the fighters themselves be directed at those in the struggle, or will these weapons fall into the hands of some underworld gangs and commit any crime, therefore, the young people who are engaged in the struggle for the future should act with utmost caution and patience at this time. have to",
        "It cannot be said that Ayuda lost his life as a step in another conspiracy. The solution that we see is to give the responsibility to the parliament democratically according to the constitution and find a solution through the parliament. Showed the strength of our struggle. Showed the strength of the people. Demonstrated people's sovereignty."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
